<abstract><t>In-situ Flow Information Telemetry (iFIT) is a framework for applying techniques such as In-situ OAM (iOAM) and Postcard-Based Telemetry (PBT) in networks.  It enumerates several key components and describes how these components can be assembled to achieve a complete working solution for user traffic telemetry in carrier networks.</t></abstract>

